01:06:55.141 --> 01:06:56.768
Sim, sim, relaxa.

01:06:57.729 --> 01:06:59.093
Tem calma.

01:06:59.199 --> 01:07:00.510
Nasha!

01:07:00.604 --> 01:07:02.415
